```csharp
using Pulumi;
using AliCloud = Pulumi.AliCloud;

class MyStack : Stack

    public MyStack()
    {
        // Create a new action trail.

        {
            EventRw = "Write-test",
            OssBucketName = alicloud_oss_bucket.Bucket.Id,
            OssKeyPrefix = "at-product-account-audit-B",
            RoleName = alicloud_ram_role_policy_attachment.Attach.Role_name,
        });
    }

}
```
